{"tid":1599022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救俾人呃","createTime":"2019-09-27T17:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T00:01:14.000Z","uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"595b418c211174d05268c341ecd4418c87c91705","tid":1599022,"uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:52:00.000Z","msg":"小弟自認衰鹹濕 衰on9<br />\n喺app度識咗個女仔<br />\n俾佢點左上尖沙咀賭船<br />\n之後俾啲古惑仔逼我賭錢然後輸咗一萬蚊<br />\n之後仲要簽咗張借據打埋手指模<br />\n嗰一萬蚊我都當算啦當買個教訓<br />\n但係之後我還返錢俾佢仲有冇手尾要跟？<br />\n有冇巴打有類似嘅經驗<br />\n又或者可以搵邊到尋求協助<br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddd091aa1a2b3a0cbc8c1200dd72ebe81c8a4c1","tid":1599022,"uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T17:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620bb0b938c0cb120a75d668112561295c3d1158","tid":1599022,"uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:09:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20420191fa3cead3c7dbaf3ff3231b783e0e0ad7","tid":1599022,"uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf029ea67421fca95acbb1b54e6b2a0d28530313","tid":1599022,"uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T18:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cea2c4a58fe00907b761d446ddc8dae3f76c33","tid":1599022,"uid":72267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T23:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f348c4c440f575e6205784a59758a459fa4176c1","tid":1599022,"uid":186074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T00:01:14.000Z","msg":"詳細描述點樣逼你賭先?"}]}